---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
---

<Layout title="Iterative Research">
  <main>
    <div class="logo">
      <picture>
        <source srcset="logo.webp" type="image/webp" />
        <source srcset="logo.png" type="image/png" />
        <img
          src="logo.png"
          alt="Iterative Research Inc."
          class="m-auto aspect-auto"
        />
      </picture>
    </div>
    <h1>
      Turning hard problems into <span class="text-gradient"
        >predictable solutions</span
      >
    </h1>

    <ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
      <Card
        title="Experimental Development"
        body="Transform complex and uncertain software engineering projects into guaranteed, predictable outcomes by letting us take the lead"
        exaggerate="...and the risk."
      >
        <h3>De-risk Complex Projects with Confidence</h3>

        <p>
          Complex software engineering projects come with layers of uncertainty,
          and you're balancing budgets, approvals, and accountability. That’s
          where we come in. Our model has us take the risk of delivery,
          transforming high-risk, high-complexity projects into streamlined,
          predictable outcomes.
        </p>

        <p>
          We iterate fast, expect feedback and participation from you, and then
          adapt quickly, letting us discover the right solution while giving you
          control without the risk, guiding your project from concept to
          completion, with full transparency and guaranteed results.
        </p>

        <Card
          title="Optimized Outcomes"
          body="Leverage cutting-edge experimentation techniques for conversion rate optimization, recommender systems, business model innovation, or any other learning-while-earning challenges."
        >
          <h3>Optimized Outcomes with Data-Driven Experimentation</h3>

          <p>
            Harness the power of machine learning, multi-armed bandit
            optimization, and advanced analytical techniques to transform your
            decision-making process. With expertise rooted in research and
            real-world application, we help you tackle critical challenges while
            learning and improving every step of the way.
          </p>

          <p>Here’s how we can support your goals:</p>

          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Conversion Rate Optimization:</strong> Continuously refine
              strategies with real-time experiments to improve conversions and customer
              journeys.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Recommender Systems:</strong> Deploy adaptive, personalized
              recommendations that evolve with user behavior, maximizing engagement
              and satisfaction.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Business Model Innovation:</strong> Safely test new approaches,
              validating revenue streams and strategic pivots with minimal risk.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Primary Data Collection & Survey Administration:</strong> Design,
              execute, and analyze studies that provide actionable insights while
              maintaining high data integrity.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Advanced Analytics & Experimentation:</strong> Use experimentation
              frameworks to optimize everything from A/B tests to market segmentation,
              ensuring every decision is backed by robust data.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <p>
            Our comprehensive approach combines innovation with precision,
            delivering reliable, data-driven outcomes for any analytical or
            optimization challenge you face.
          </p>
        </Card>
        <Card
          title="Engineering Excellence"
          body="Bring your software engineering operations to the next level with our expert strategic guidance—team performance, effective, joyful process, and industry-leading quality automation."
        >
          <strong
            >Engineering Excellence, Tailored to Meet You Where You Are</strong
          >

          <p>
            Take your software engineering operations to the next level with
            in-depth reviews and data-driven recommendations, powered by our
            proprietary tool. We analyze how your team and organization are
            performing across critical areas and provide expert insights on
            where to improve—without the need for us to build anything.
          </p>

          <p>
            You’ll get actionable guidance, ready to implement and we'll be
            there to help with the transformation necessary to implement
            effectively. <strong
              >We'll help you make your engineering operations exceptional.</strong
            >
          </p>

          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>CI/CD Effectiveness:</strong> We assess your current integration
              and delivery pipelines and offer precise recommendations to optimize
              deployment efficiency and reliability.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Code Review Quality:</strong> Gain an expert evaluation of
              your code review processes, with feedback on how to improve quality,
              speed, and team collaboration.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Testing and Quality Systems:</strong> We review your testing
              frameworks and provide recommendations for increasing automation and
              enhancing software reliability.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Performance Metrics:</strong> Get a thorough review of how
              you’re measuring success with tailored advice on performance indicators
              that drive technical, product, HR and overall organizational excellence.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Career Development and Retention:</strong> We assess your career
              development structures, team satisfication and needs, and offer strategic
              recommendations to help your engineers grow and thrive.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <p>
            We meet you where you’re at, delivering expert strategic guidance in
            the areas you need most. Whether you're fine-tuning CI/CD pipelines
            or enhancing team dynamics, we’ll walk with you every step of the
            way to ensure your engineering operations are built for long-term
            success.
          </p>
        </Card>
        <Card
          title="Systematic Review"
          body="Comprehensive reviews and insights for diligence, for management, or just external eyes for technical leads to help understand, document and improve your software engineering operations—code, security, architecture, or processes."
        >
          <p>
            From formal diligence to strategic insights, we can provide a
            actionable evaluation that ensures you're not only compliant but
            also positioned for long-term success.
          </p>

          <ul class="list-style-disc">
            <li>
              <strong>Security Review:</strong> Meet and exceed your current compliance
              needs while proactively securing your systems with our expert security
              audits.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Privacy Impact Analysis:</strong> Ensure your business manages
              privacy expectations with precision, mitigating risk and safeguarding
              sensitive data.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Strategic Recommendations:</strong> Receive expert, high-level
              guidance tailored to your organization’s needs, helping you optimize
              for scale, performance, and sustainability.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Holistic Code Review:</strong> Our unbiased, in-depth code
              review gets you outside eyes to assist engineering and provide recommendations
              to help resolve your biggest challenges.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Architecture & Process Review:</strong> Evaluate your systems’
              architecture and processes, and receive targeted recommendations to
              streamline workflows and boost productivity.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <p>
            Sometimes it is about checking boxes—whether for management, board
            reviews, or regulatory requirements—but we go further, helping you
            turn compliance into an opportunity for growth. Our reviews provide
            clarity and confidence for every stakeholder, from your technical
            leads to top-level executives.
          </p>1
        </Card>
      </Card>
    </ul>

    <div class="call-to-action">
      Do you have an uncertainty to explore, an experiment, data-driven
      optimization or software engineering challenge that you need help with? <a
        href="mailto:contact@iterative.ca">Contact us</a
      > to discuss how we can help.
    </div>
    <footer>&copy; Iterative Research Inc.</footer>
  </main>

  <style>
    main {
      margin: auto;
      padding: 1rem;
      padding-top: 0;
      /* _Negative margin considered harmful_, crop the logo instead. */
      margin-top: -1.5rem;
      width: 800px;
      max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
      color: white;
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.6em;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1;
      text-align: center;
      text-wrap: balance;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .logo {
      height: 33vh;
      max-height: fit-content;
      margin: 0 auto;
      overflow: hidden;

      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
      }
      .logo {
        height: 25vh;
      }
    }
    .text-gradient {
      background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-size: 400%;
      background-position: 0%;
    }
    .link-card-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(24ch, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: 0;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
    }

    .call-to-action {
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;

      text-align: center;
      text-wrap: balance;
    }
    .call-to-action a {
      color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .call-to-action a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
